Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:53.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母亲  母亲正在看着呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}竟然被这种粗糙的箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:21.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:26.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}保护着我辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然是段短暂的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人  给您水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没事  给神奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是我的命令  喝了它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就剩这些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了  三个人分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把剩下的全喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:24.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样三个人靠在一起  简直
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就像是一个和睦的家庭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「真正的家族就是紧密地靠在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这话不是你说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}的确是那样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你们两个有什么愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么突然问起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊 突然被你这么一问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:51.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算拼了命  也要冲出包围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}至少也要让神奈活着逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的话有个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想和神奈大人与柳也大人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永远生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也许是个不错的愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在某个宁静的地方  搭建一个小小的庵堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}养家糊口的话  我是可以想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}种地也好  打猎也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果是在海边的话  还也可以打鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:20.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}非要去的话  西边的暖海应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海  是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听人说是一个宽广无尽的大水池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过没有亲眼见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然是一个水池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过里面的水都是盐水哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又在骗我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是真的  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且  海和天空一样宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}鲷鱼和鲍鱼也可以随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就要看我能捞回多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:05.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海边的小村中也会举行夏日祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  在哪都会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下回我们三个人一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}光看没有意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}梦也不全是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你们两个绝对不可以离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:39.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与柳也在一起  我都忘记了自己的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是我最后的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你们要永远的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:00.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要怕！放箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是降魔的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:34.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}法师们正在向神奈大人施法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直念下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了消灭翼人  保卫这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要怕牺牲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈 再飞高点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再高点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再飞高点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:50.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳… 也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:22.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈—！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人 您要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把神奈弄成这样的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我死前能杀一个是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拦着我的话就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就请杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可不是在吓唬你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到变成恶鬼的柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  我还能听到神奈大人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:05.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:06.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过我可以听到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以听到神奈大人的哭声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想你们是神奈备命的护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}奉师傅之命  来迎接你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}召见我们的  是一位叫智德法师的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}智德对神奈的事大概都已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这做寺院中也曾经住过翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从那以后  这个寺院就成为了看护翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}时而也会援助翼人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}按照智德的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}翼人们代代相传着星之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:52.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从很早以前就开始  传授了人类很多知识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其中的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是现在我们所说的法术的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么叫继承梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个  我们无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正因为翼人有这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以经常被掌权者控制起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}渐渐成为了战争的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是一个人承受了在战争中杀死的人们的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所谓的「不净」就是这个含义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}攻入灵山的是朝廷的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}说是为了毁灭「翼人」这种信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}统一人们的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}智德说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也许神奈就是这个世界上最后一个翼人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}智德大师  我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}请您无论如何将法术传授给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}于是我们便在这个寺院中住了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}据说里叶是百年一见的奇才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样过了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那么  开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}招魂的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}使用这个咒语后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就应该可以看到神奈大人在做什么样的梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也你起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么不动  为什么不抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不允许把我留下一个人离去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:33.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:37.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么大家  只留下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈在做的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是说她正在天空中的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直做着这样的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}灵山僧侣们施展的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}现在依然折磨着神奈大人的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}此外还有她从母亲那继承下来的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:13.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这些都会另与翼人亲近的人渐渐衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久便会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的伤口总无法复原也是这个原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:22.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我自己可以施法避开那些诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但柳也大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的死期是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从现在开始  撑不了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:37.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}禁锢着神奈大人的咒语终有一天会瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:43.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时神奈大人的灵魂会回归大地  轮回转生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过  把翼人的灵魂注入人类的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就好比让一个小的容器去承受大海的水量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:55.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}水还没有注完  容器就破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以神奈大人的灵魂还无法得到复原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就再次轮回转生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经没有多少时日了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有什么解救神奈的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}办法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}请留下一个孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人的意志就可以传乘下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果我们的孩子依然没能完成  还有孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}孙子也没能完成的话  还有曾孙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们都会继承柳也大人的意志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:33.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后终有一天会找到解救神奈大人的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我来帮助您…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:43.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:48.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我生命中剩余的时间会全部用在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}时光缓缓流逝着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:57.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}石屋里有我编写的「翼人传」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:02.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久即将出生的我们的孩子  寻找神奈的灵魂时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这本书一定可以成为他的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后里叶会教他法术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果是继承着里叶的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一定会成为擅长法术的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也许可以最终找到我们没能想到的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:21.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要时光流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的旅途就能继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了寻找那对无可取代的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了能再次与她相见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经没有什么可留恋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}鸟在飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:42.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算忘记也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘记神奈也忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幸福的生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为我不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人和柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今后也会在身边为我指引道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这才是我的妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢谢你… 里叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下雨了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明明是晴空万里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  里叶我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:36.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈在天空的彼岸等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的  我陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海角天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:57.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:20:59.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才为止我一直在什么人的身旁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在一个重要的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:09.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}脑子空空的想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:26.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  你是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:27.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还不会飞吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:37.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 留下它就这样走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧  走几步回头看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有跟过来的话就拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！ 跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要和我一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊  那一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:01.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}走喽～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:42.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明天开始就放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这东西还和你真亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我给他起名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:47.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫小空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:49.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就没有别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不许
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:58.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}总不能一直这样生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:01.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就无法努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:07.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我出去一下
